hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: An estate agents mountaineer brand beard oil Cook, God bless him, is so sedate, I think he’s scaring investors, and the Apple faithful alike. Cook seems like the Mel Torme to Job’s Sinatra; Hutch to Starsky; fish and chips to Sushi. The lack of hype and zeal about new products, like the iPhone 5′s debut last September, seems noticeably absent. I think this is giving people pause in their perspective of Apple as the scrappy startup Steve Jobs embodied and cultivated. Under Jobs, Apple had the feel and image of the underdog, daring to take on the tech Goliaths. They need that again.
